message.body: We had just started our hike to the lake when your txt came in...1:47 now. Enjoy Nashville
Thank you! Got delayed in Baltimore but just landed in Nashville...and unknowingly gained an hour!
Thank you! We just sat down at Robert's western world...
JD must have some wicked callouses...did you buy their cd when you were down here?
Yes...is he not one of the best live guitarists you' ve ever seen?
I'll send you the cd if you like
Well I don't have much to compare to but he's incredible...the bassist is amazing as well. Ahh okay we were going to pick you up a signed one if you didn't already have it
Couldn't resist...it was the only music we bought there...not even my style...
